{"tid":417394,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"屋企人同你既關係，有無影響你嘅擇偶條件？","createTime":"2017-09-28T15:23:57.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-28T16:31:53.000Z","uid":18271,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"a0df9efc6cd547bf695adb725fef5030955adc7b","tid":417394,"uid":18271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-28T15:23:57.000Z","msg":"我目標係搵一個同我老母性格相反既女人做女友<br />\n自細我係單親家庭<br />\n不過我老母自細就唔鍾意我，同佢關係非常差<br />\n自我中心、無知、霸道、雙重標準、監控狂、嘴賤就講晒佢個人<br />\n以前成日會同佢嘈<br />\n但人大左已經好多野煩<br />\n都無謂同佢一般見識<br />\n除左唔返屋企食飯基本上都唔多想同佢講野<br />\n但佢永遠要搵d小事嚟搵野嘈<br />\n<br />\n我覺得我搵女友一定唔可以似佢任何缺點<br />\n否則我覺得我下半世都係玩完<br />\n有無人同我差唔多？"},{"pid":"51df013775765f6e5457b561e0aec67074c7ac4c","tid":417394,"uid":119401,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-28T15:30:41.000Z","msg":"D缺點係因為無男人係身邊而導致你點睇?<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n老女人無人愛錫好似會失平衡咁癲癲地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0764a3a358dca5ea271262da414e9fd68881dbb7","tid":417394,"uid":18271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-28T15:35:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>D缺點係因為無男人係身邊而導致你點睇?<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n老女人無人愛錫好似會失平衡咁癲癲地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咁唔代表佢可以精神虐待我<br />\n就算我老豆在生嗰時佢都係好唔鍾意我<br />\n由細到大都鬧我蠢<br />\n成世人讚我次數一隻手數完"},{"pid":"733d4a5b71f6fb402d0f208a6c5fea765b0719fa","tid":417394,"uid":18271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-28T15:43:34.000Z","msg":"分享下啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f8ecabd75f38ebdd12718273abfb1027d6f42563","tid":417394,"uid":119401,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-28T15:55:42.000Z","msg":"深入咁傾溝通下應該解決到<br />\n煩係煩D架啦，加油"},{"pid":"1a8ca48cfc73a4543d36367cee8188f8e90e760d","tid":417394,"uid":18271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-28T16:09:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>深入咁傾溝通下應該解決到<br />\n煩係煩D架啦，加油</blockquote><br />\n細個試過<br />\n你讓步只會恰到你上心口<br />\n不了"},{"pid":"237337ca676ec1d7e87c8aa2e517d29ad2a87772","tid":417394,"uid":41356,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-28T16:20:06.000Z","msg":"直頭唔想拍拖<br />\n見到老豆就覺得佢中咗伏"},{"pid":"255bf94d1498702c727ebc1e5dd4419c9ed0544e","tid":417394,"uid":18271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-28T16:31:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>直頭唔想拍拖<br />\n見到老豆就覺得佢中咗伏</blockquote><br />\n咁你老豆眼光差啫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}